x4freetext: Energy spead of incident beam set at 30 keV (FWHM).
Measured relative cross sections, and normalized using
monitor counter set up at 90 degrees.
Points at 60, 70, 80, and 90 degrees were measured
twice to check internal consistancy.
Corrected for counting losses, and background.
Normalization uncertainty.
Relative uncertainty.
Approved by G. Crawley, 11 May 2000.
Data taken from thesis.
VM
